1
00:00:18,310 --> 00:00:25,030
♫ As dusk starts, I look at the setting sun in the horizon ♫

2
00:00:25,030 --> 00:00:30,620
♫  I faintly remember the outline of your face ♫

3
00:00:30,620 --> 00:00:37,330
♫  After all, it can't be helped to feel more sentimental
when one reminisces  ♫

4
00:00:37,330 --> 00:00:45,300
♫  I sigh softly at our happy times ♫

5
00:00:45,300 --> 00:00:51,740
♫  The night hasn't ended, so many stars fall into the
rim of my eyes  ♫

6
00:00:51,740 --> 00:00:57,470
♫  Collecting a soft and gentle light  ♫

7
00:00:57,470 --> 00:01:00,940
♫ The sky is clear, the scenery are good ♫

8
00:01:00,940 --> 00:01:05,130
♫ If you're not by my side♫

9
00:01:05,130 --> 00:01:11,090
♫ So what if I can go up the Firmament ♫

10
00:01:11,090 --> 00:01:18,020
♫ The boat passes an empty harbor and feeds the loneliness ♫

11
00:01:18,020 --> 00:01:24,560
♫ Frost falls over the wilderness, drooping the tears ♫

12
00:01:24,560 --> 00:01:28,830
♫ Who caused my sun to fall from the sky ♫

13
00:01:28,830 --> 00:01:39,270
♫ It’s your face that took away my entire light ♫

14
00:01:39,270 --> 00:01:45,710
♫  For only you are my heaven ♫

15
00:01:45,710 --> 00:01:51,630
[Goodbye My Princess]

16
00:01:51,630 --> 00:01:56,530
[Episode 54]

17
00:02:08,310 --> 00:02:13,700
[Bearing Graces Hall]

18
00:02:18,910 --> 00:02:21,450
Yongniang, your hands are very fragrant.

19
00:02:23,440 --> 00:02:26,010
Like my mother's.

20
00:02:28,860 --> 00:02:32,480
I remember you were terribly sick when you first came to the palace.

21
00:02:32,480 --> 00:02:35,530
You were so hot from fever every day and night.

22
00:02:35,530 --> 00:02:40,010
The imperial physicians were afraid of using random medicines in case something bad happened to you.

23
00:02:40,700 --> 00:02:43,810
I stayed with you all the time.

24
00:02:45,030 --> 00:02:48,320
You didn't speak the Central Plains language well at that time.

25
00:02:48,320 --> 00:02:51,340
While dreaming, you kept saying that you want "shanzi."

26
00:02:51,340 --> 00:02:53,370
"I want shanzi."

27
00:02:54,930 --> 00:02:57,360
Later, I came to understand that

28
00:02:57,360 --> 00:03:01,760
"shanzi" meant mom in the Xi State language.

29
00:03:14,960 --> 00:03:17,920
In a blink of an eye, it's been over two years.

30
00:03:17,920 --> 00:03:21,720
Crown Princess Consort, you are already an 18-year-old adult.

31
00:03:22,330 --> 00:03:27,060
In the future, you must not be willful and boisterous anymore.

32
00:03:29,560 --> 00:03:31,870
I will listen to you.

33
00:03:32,360 --> 00:03:34,150
In the future,

34
00:03:34,990 --> 00:03:37,770
I will not be willful and boisterous anymore.

35
00:04:12,710 --> 00:04:14,580
Where's His Highness?

36
00:04:18,420 --> 00:04:21,020
[Qingluan Hall]

37
00:05:33,710 --> 00:05:36,660
You're playing such a sorrowful melody,

38
00:05:40,120 --> 00:05:43,140
as if everyone has betrayed you.

39
00:05:48,700 --> 00:05:51,430
I can betray everyone,

40
00:05:52,240 --> 00:05:55,150
but I do not wish to betray you again.

41
00:06:00,900 --> 00:06:04,070
But you are not worthy of anyone's love.

42
00:06:04,960 --> 00:06:08,030
If you had a little bit of humanity in you,

43
00:06:08,030 --> 00:06:11,420
you wouldn't have said those words to Lady Zhao.

44
00:06:12,910 --> 00:06:17,350
Love has always been not worth a cent at all in front of you.

45
00:06:20,610 --> 00:06:24,020
Power must be what you truly want to pursue in your life.

46
00:06:37,410 --> 00:06:39,260
Xiaofeng,

47
00:06:40,360 --> 00:06:43,050
you are actually the only one I want in my life.

48
00:06:46,190 --> 00:06:49,350
You used to like Lady Zhao so much.

49
00:06:49,350 --> 00:06:52,360
You argued with me every day because of her.

50
00:06:52,360 --> 00:06:55,540
But now, you say you've been using her.

51
00:06:56,280 --> 00:06:58,850
You originally hated me so much,

52
00:06:58,850 --> 00:07:01,530
telling me every day that you wanted to divorce me.

53
00:07:02,320 --> 00:07:06,320
But now, you say that I am the only thing you want in your life.

54
00:07:06,320 --> 00:07:10,750
How do you expect me to believe someone like you?

55
00:07:12,870 --> 00:07:14,940
You do not understand.

56
00:07:15,500 --> 00:07:19,200
A lot of things... were out of my control.

57
00:07:19,240 --> 00:07:21,370
You are forever being forced to do things beyond your control.

58
00:07:21,370 --> 00:07:23,570
Your explanations

59
00:07:23,570 --> 00:07:26,630
will never be able to answer my questions.

60
00:07:31,180 --> 00:07:33,140
If one day,

61
00:07:33,140 --> 00:07:36,810
I endanger your throne, your land, your imperial court,

62
00:07:36,810 --> 00:07:39,200
will you kill me?

63
00:07:41,900 --> 00:07:46,250
The Eastern Palace is even more dangerous than the imperial court.

64
00:07:48,660 --> 00:07:52,070
Being the crown prince is even harder than being the emperor.

65
00:07:52,590 --> 00:07:56,480
- You didn't know all the hardships that I endured along this journey.
- Will you...

66
00:07:57,690 --> 00:08:00,190
one day kill me, too?

67
00:08:02,280 --> 00:08:05,230
Xiaofeng, I will not kill you.

68
00:08:05,230 --> 00:08:07,670
I will not allow anyone to hurt you either.

69
00:08:07,670 --> 00:08:10,920
I will treat you well. I will be good to you for a lifetime!

70
00:08:10,920 --> 00:08:12,600
I beg you,

71
00:08:12,600 --> 00:08:17,070
even if you do not like me, even if your heart does not even have an ounce of me in it, it is fine.

72
00:08:17,510 --> 00:08:19,870
If I wanted you to

73
00:08:19,870 --> 00:08:23,140
let go of the emperor's position that you're so close to obtaining now,

74
00:08:23,140 --> 00:08:27,700
and die with me, would you be willing?

75
00:08:27,700 --> 00:08:31,560
Why must you still speak of death?! We will both not die!

76
00:08:31,560 --> 00:08:36,800
We will not die! Everything has settled down. There are only you and me now.

77
00:08:37,700 --> 00:08:39,620
You are not willing.

78
00:08:46,130 --> 00:08:49,360
Then, will you only believe my words

79
00:08:49,360 --> 00:08:52,120
once you have seen me dead?

80
00:08:53,460 --> 00:08:55,490
You will not die.

81
00:08:57,900 --> 00:09:00,620
You will live well.

82
00:09:01,670 --> 00:09:06,400
But you will not be by my side, right?

83
00:09:12,830 --> 00:09:14,860
I really hate...

84
00:09:15,510 --> 00:09:18,690
really hate that the person in your heart is not me.

85
00:09:19,680 --> 00:09:21,380
Why?

86
00:09:28,350 --> 00:09:30,130
Why?

87
00:09:35,430 --> 00:09:37,300
Li Chengyin,

88
00:09:42,080 --> 00:09:44,430
actually my heart...

89
00:09:45,080 --> 00:09:47,390
has always had you in it.

90
00:10:03,710 --> 00:10:06,010
What did you say just now? What did you say?

91
00:10:06,010 --> 00:10:09,710
Say it again! Say it again!

92
00:10:13,900 --> 00:10:18,510
What I said just now, I really hate...

93
00:10:18,510 --> 00:10:22,250
really hate that my heart has always had you in it.

94
00:10:28,460 --> 00:10:30,600
With these words,

95
00:10:31,150 --> 00:10:33,450
even if I die,

96
00:10:34,550 --> 00:10:36,570
I am contented.

97
00:10:44,650 --> 00:10:47,470
I am telling you this today...

98
00:10:49,870 --> 00:10:53,310
because I am going to say goodbye to you.

99
00:11:00,200 --> 00:11:02,070
Goodbye,

100
00:11:04,830 --> 00:11:06,720
my...

101
00:11:09,120 --> 00:11:11,890
Gu Xiaowu.

102
00:11:28,320 --> 00:11:31,590
The sedating drug of Dashi State is really strong.

103
00:11:32,200 --> 00:11:34,300
When he wakes up,

104
00:11:36,680 --> 00:11:39,110
we will have already left the palace.

105
00:12:20,770 --> 00:12:22,520
Yongniang.

106
00:12:24,480 --> 00:12:28,620
What do we do? If Yongniang doesn't leave, the Yulin Palace Guards will soon get here.

107
00:12:28,620 --> 00:12:30,550
At that time,

108
00:12:30,550 --> 00:12:32,660
we really will not be able to escape.

109
00:12:37,580 --> 00:12:39,530
You wait here for me.

110
00:13:06,600 --> 00:13:10,560
Yongniang, Xiaofeng is leaving.

111
00:13:16,940 --> 00:13:18,900
I will miss you.

112
00:13:26,980 --> 00:13:28,590
Princess.

113
00:13:53,580 --> 00:13:55,620
I thought...

114
00:13:57,410 --> 00:13:59,650
that you would not let me leave.

115
00:14:02,740 --> 00:14:05,340
But you were actually here waiting for me.

116
00:14:09,790 --> 00:14:12,320
In the past, I always thought that

117
00:14:13,180 --> 00:14:16,970
you would only allow me to memorize books, learn rules,

118
00:14:16,970 --> 00:14:19,080
and curry favor with others.

119
00:14:19,080 --> 00:14:21,570
I thought you did not understand me.

120
00:14:27,960 --> 00:14:31,720
Princess, we must hurry and leave.

121
00:14:31,720 --> 00:14:34,280
If we do not leave now, it will be too late.

122
00:14:40,880 --> 00:14:44,080
A'Du, unblock Yongniang's acupoints.

123
00:14:46,010 --> 00:14:47,800
Hurry!

124
00:14:53,770 --> 00:14:57,180
Maybe, it's best for Yongniang this way.

125
00:15:17,510 --> 00:15:19,480
It's cold at night.

126
00:15:22,360 --> 00:15:24,160
Sorry to make you suffer.

127
00:15:30,500 --> 00:15:32,600
Princess...

128
00:16:33,200 --> 00:16:34,970
Mi Luo!

129
00:16:41,080 --> 00:16:42,830
You are finally here.

130
00:16:42,830 --> 00:16:45,280
I was so worried and afraid that

131
00:16:45,280 --> 00:16:47,540
you couldn't make it here today.

132
00:16:47,540 --> 00:16:50,420
I was also not sure before I got here today.

133
00:16:51,050 --> 00:16:53,400
I'm glad we finally made it out.

134
00:16:54,500 --> 00:16:56,710
You weren't discovered, were you?

135
00:17:01,440 --> 00:17:03,540
What's wrong?

136
00:17:03,540 --> 00:17:06,600
Is there still anything that you can't bear to leave?

137
00:17:09,340 --> 00:17:12,170
It was only until I was leaving that I discovered

138
00:17:14,550 --> 00:17:19,500
there are people who truly cared for me in the Eastern Palace.

139
00:17:20,390 --> 00:17:22,880
There are also people that I feel sorry to.

140
00:17:24,750 --> 00:17:28,650
Xaiofeng, since you've made your decision,

141
00:17:28,650 --> 00:17:31,370
then don't hesitate and drag it further.

142
00:17:31,370 --> 00:17:34,980
Princess, Yongniang won't blame you.

143
00:17:37,300 --> 00:17:39,280
In that palace,

144
00:17:39,750 --> 00:17:42,810
besides hurting your heart, your health,

145
00:17:42,810 --> 00:17:46,320
even your life, there is nothing to gain.

146
00:17:46,320 --> 00:17:49,640
You have to leave in order to keep yourself alive.

147
00:17:49,640 --> 00:17:53,450
Come, let me explain the plan to help you leave the city.

148
00:17:54,470 --> 00:17:56,560
- All right.
- Princess, sit.

149
00:18:31,560 --> 00:18:35,380
Xiaofeng... Xiaofeng?

150
00:18:35,380 --> 00:18:38,740
Xiaofeng! Xiaofeng!

151
00:18:38,740 --> 00:18:40,990
Guards! Guards!

152
00:18:44,540 --> 00:18:47,310
- Xiaofeng!
- Your Imperial Highness?

153
00:18:47,820 --> 00:18:51,740
- Crown Princess Consort! Where is the Crown Princess Consort?
- Crown Princess Consort?

154
00:18:51,740 --> 00:18:55,030
Wasn't she with you?

155
00:18:58,450 --> 00:19:00,170
Your Imperial Highness!

156
00:19:01,080 --> 00:19:06,640
Xiaofeng! Xiaofeng!

157
00:19:08,060 --> 00:19:13,450
Xiaofeng!

158
00:19:17,080 --> 00:19:18,610
Xiaofeng!

159
00:19:22,770 --> 00:19:24,520
Xiaofeng!

160
00:19:30,530 --> 00:19:32,150
Xiaofeng!

161
00:19:34,480 --> 00:19:39,270
Your Imperial Highness, Yongniang stood outside the whole night because her pressure points were locked.

162
00:19:42,300 --> 00:19:46,170
- Where is Crown Princess Consort?
- Forgive me, Your Imperial Highness!

163
00:19:53,370 --> 00:19:57,030
Pei Zhao, order troops to guard all the entryways and gates of the city.

164
00:19:57,030 --> 00:19:59,690
Anyone who is leaving the city and the border

165
00:19:59,690 --> 00:20:01,610
must be checked thoroughly.

166
00:20:01,610 --> 00:20:05,160
Post the portraits of Crown Princess Consort everywhere. You must get me Xiaofeng back!

167
00:20:05,160 --> 00:20:06,690
Yes.

168
00:20:12,210 --> 00:20:13,840
Move away! Move away!

169
00:20:16,070 --> 00:20:17,780
Move away! Move away!

170
00:20:19,520 --> 00:20:23,320
- Go.
- You can go. Come, you're next.

171
00:20:28,850 --> 00:20:32,780
Out of the nine gates of Shangjing city, the Western Gate has the tightest security.

172
00:20:32,780 --> 00:20:35,880
They will definitely think you'd leave from another gate.

173
00:20:35,880 --> 00:20:39,470
We will do the opposite and leave through the Western Gate.

174
00:20:39,470 --> 00:20:42,180
A Goryeo caravan will be leaving the city tomorrow morning.

175
00:20:42,180 --> 00:20:44,500
I've bribed the leader to smuggle you out.

176
00:20:44,500 --> 00:20:48,810
- Guard Commander, we are a Goryeo caravan passing by your land.
- Okay.

177
00:20:48,810 --> 00:20:50,380
Let them through.

178
00:21:02,950 --> 00:21:04,890
General Pei!

179
00:21:10,400 --> 00:21:13,300
What's this about?

180
00:21:13,300 --> 00:21:17,340
The crown princess consort has run away. Did she come to your place?

181
00:21:19,460 --> 00:21:22,930
Are you suspecting that she had been here,

182
00:21:22,930 --> 00:21:25,830
or are you thinking that she is inside now?

183
00:21:28,890 --> 00:21:32,690
If you really want to find someone at my place,

184
00:21:32,690 --> 00:21:35,020
just go ahead and crash in to search.

185
00:21:35,020 --> 00:21:39,240
You don't need to stand in front of my wine house

186
00:21:39,240 --> 00:21:41,680
and ask me such a question.

187
00:21:41,680 --> 00:21:43,950
I think that in your heart,

188
00:21:43,950 --> 00:21:47,950
you also don't want Xiaofeng to return to that Eastern Palace.

189
00:21:47,950 --> 00:21:53,260
You think too much. I am only searching for the crown princess consort as ordered by the crown prince.

190
00:21:53,880 --> 00:21:55,330
Okay.

191
00:21:55,830 --> 00:21:58,970
I'll tell you then that she did come,

192
00:21:58,970 --> 00:22:02,160
- but has already left..
- Where is she?

193
00:22:02,160 --> 00:22:04,750
That, I don't know.

194
00:22:06,170 --> 00:22:09,420
But... does the general

195
00:22:09,420 --> 00:22:12,260
really want to know?

196
00:22:17,490 --> 00:22:21,610
- Give money. Give money.
- Didn't Mi Luo already give you?

197
00:22:21,610 --> 00:22:24,150
This matter is so serious!

198
00:22:24,150 --> 00:22:26,430
You need to add more money.

199
00:22:27,160 --> 00:22:30,080
More money or I'll tell the guards.

200
00:22:48,240 --> 00:22:50,400
Come! Come inside.
[Datong Relay Station]

201
00:22:51,130 --> 00:22:53,640
Come! Follow me. Come.

202
00:22:54,350 --> 00:22:56,530
We are staying here tonight.

203
00:22:56,530 --> 00:22:59,720
Follow me. Go

204
00:23:00,450 --> 00:23:01,940
Go.

205
00:23:04,400 --> 00:23:06,210
A'Du, look!

206
00:23:07,520 --> 00:23:09,790
[Wanted Criminals]

207
00:23:10,810 --> 00:23:12,940
Probably, the Jade Pass

208
00:23:12,940 --> 00:23:15,190
is full of troops waiting for us now.

209
00:23:15,190 --> 00:23:19,070
Why don't we not exit through the Jade Pass? Let's go out through another way?

210
00:23:20,470 --> 00:23:23,160
[Wanted Criminals]

211
00:23:23,680 --> 00:23:25,870
Since Li Chengyin wants to capture me,

212
00:23:25,870 --> 00:23:28,870
no matter where I go, he will have set up a trap.

213
00:23:30,450 --> 00:23:32,590
Since we've already chosen this path,

214
00:23:32,590 --> 00:23:35,110
let's follow through. At worst, we die.

215
00:23:35,110 --> 00:23:36,850
All right.

216
00:23:40,200 --> 00:23:51,500
[Datong Relay Station]

217
00:23:52,900 --> 00:23:54,880
A'Du, are you ready?

218
00:23:54,880 --> 00:23:58,180
Princess, I'm ready.

219
00:23:58,180 --> 00:24:02,040
Let's leave before they wake up, so they won't report it to the authorities.

220
00:24:02,040 --> 00:24:03,580
All right.

221
00:24:14,270 --> 00:24:16,650
Princess, go.

222
00:24:25,400 --> 00:24:31,360
[Gathering Cloud Building]

223
00:24:37,830 --> 00:24:43,630
[Gu Jian of the Family of Gu's Tombstone]

224
00:24:55,880 --> 00:24:59,470
Drunken Cat, I've brought

225
00:24:59,470 --> 00:25:01,510
your favorite "Out in Half a Pot."

226
00:25:04,220 --> 00:25:06,410
Over there,

227
00:25:08,110 --> 00:25:11,130
you probably don't have as many worries, right?

228
00:25:14,430 --> 00:25:16,480
I need to leave now.

229
00:25:20,620 --> 00:25:22,610
This Shangjing City...

230
00:25:24,270 --> 00:25:28,180
doesn't have anything worth yearning for.

231
00:25:33,970 --> 00:25:36,030
You said before...

232
00:25:37,470 --> 00:25:40,160
that we were both people in distress,
(T/N: Literal translation is " Fallen people at the end of the world")

233
00:25:41,080 --> 00:25:44,820
You've fallen to this, yet I

234
00:25:46,200 --> 00:25:48,420
am going to the end of the world.

235
00:25:57,960 --> 00:26:02,480
[Gu Jian of the Family of Gu's Tombstone]

236
00:26:47,840 --> 00:26:51,820
[Jade Pass]

237
00:27:03,240 --> 00:27:08,200
[Jade Pass]

238
00:27:20,420 --> 00:27:22,250
It's Pei Zhao.

239
00:27:23,090 --> 00:27:24,950
Xiaofeng.

240
00:27:47,620 --> 00:27:50,230
- Crown Princess Consort.
- Pei Zhao.

241
00:27:50,230 --> 00:27:52,830
I heard you playing the hichiriki flute.

242
00:27:55,240 --> 00:27:59,470
Crown Princess Consort, please go back with me.

243
00:27:59,470 --> 00:28:01,860
Do you really want to persuade me to go back?

244
00:28:01,860 --> 00:28:05,470
It's my duty to escort you back to the palace.

245
00:28:05,470 --> 00:28:07,660
Let's go back.

246
00:28:07,660 --> 00:28:10,100
What difference will it make if you can return to Xi State?

247
00:28:10,100 --> 00:28:13,860
The crown prince will still send troops to Xi State and take you back to Shangjing.

248
00:28:13,860 --> 00:28:17,320
At that time, it won't be just a matter between you and him.

249
00:28:17,320 --> 00:28:20,200
It will be a matter between Xi State and Central Plains.

250
00:28:20,200 --> 00:28:24,030
But this time, I want to live for myself.

251
00:28:24,030 --> 00:28:26,680
Who doesn't want to live for himself?

252
00:28:26,680 --> 00:28:29,020
But will you really live better if you live for yourself?

253
00:28:29,020 --> 00:28:31,370
Everyone wants to pay attention to one's upright morals

254
00:28:31,370 --> 00:28:34,390
and stubbornly wants to live for oneself, but the reality

255
00:28:34,390 --> 00:28:36,050
will be even more painful.

256
00:28:36,050 --> 00:28:39,250
In the end, you'll probably discover that living for someone else

257
00:28:39,250 --> 00:28:41,750
is actually more meaningful.

258
00:28:42,790 --> 00:28:46,210
More meaningful? Won't I then have to endure pain for a whole lifetime?

259
00:28:46,210 --> 00:28:50,190
If feeling pain is for your beloved, then it's not painful.

260
00:28:50,190 --> 00:28:53,410
What about you? Who do you live for?

261
00:28:54,700 --> 00:28:56,790
Li Chengyin?

262
00:28:57,990 --> 00:28:59,780
The emperor?

263
00:29:02,450 --> 00:29:06,150
Crown Princess Consort, please go back with me.

264
00:29:07,200 --> 00:29:09,760
Perhaps, you are really living for them.

265
00:29:09,760 --> 00:29:14,760
Three years ago, you tried to help Gu Xiaowu and urged me not to jump into the River of Oblivion.

266
00:29:16,450 --> 00:29:20,870
Today, you help Li Chengyin to urge me to go back to the Eastern Palace.

267
00:29:20,870 --> 00:29:24,340
Your loyalty to him has never wavered in these three years.

268
00:29:24,340 --> 00:29:26,620
You've remembered everything.

269
00:29:31,630 --> 00:29:34,300
I remember it all.

270
00:29:34,300 --> 00:29:38,000
That's why even now if I can't escape, I will still have to try.

271
00:29:38,000 --> 00:29:39,730
To me,

272
00:29:39,730 --> 00:29:43,120
the Eastern Palace and Li Chengyin are the heaviest locks in this world.

273
00:29:43,120 --> 00:29:46,730
I really cannot bear it anymore. The person who I trust,

274
00:29:46,730 --> 00:29:51,170
the person who I love, and the people I treat as friends are all my enemies.

275
00:29:52,380 --> 00:29:56,700
- Crown Princess Consort—
- Pei Zhao, I am not the crown princess consort.

276
00:29:56,700 --> 00:29:59,470
I'm your friend. I'm Xiaofeng.

277
00:29:59,470 --> 00:30:02,300
Are you still that person whom I can trust?

278
00:30:08,020 --> 00:30:09,900
- Yes.
- Good.

279
00:30:09,900 --> 00:30:12,970
Then, today, you will let me pass. Correct?

280
00:30:20,520 --> 00:30:25,260
Pei Zhao, no matter if you allow or disallow me from leaving, I will go through the gates.

281
00:30:25,260 --> 00:30:27,150
I am even willing to accept death.

282
00:30:27,150 --> 00:30:32,360
I do not know what you are thinking about this very moment, nor do I know who you are living for.

283
00:30:32,360 --> 00:30:34,940
But when you were blowing the hichiriki on the gate tower earlier,

284
00:30:34,940 --> 00:30:37,580
you were living for yourself. Correct?

285
00:30:38,310 --> 00:30:41,820
You once did not wish to see me being lonely and being homesick.

286
00:30:41,820 --> 00:30:46,240
And today, you also do not wish to see me suffer. Correct?

287
00:30:57,400 --> 00:30:59,390
Open the city gate!

288
00:31:06,610 --> 00:31:08,450
Leave.

289
00:31:23,060 --> 00:31:24,910
[Jade Pass]

290
00:31:26,360 --> 00:31:30,860
Close the city gate!
Close the city gate!
Close the city gate!

291
00:31:33,330 --> 00:31:35,480
Close the city gate!

292
00:31:41,610 --> 00:31:43,900
Princess!

293
00:31:48,120 --> 00:31:49,950
Xiaofeng!

294
00:31:53,940 --> 00:31:57,110
Princess! Princess!

295
00:32:01,670 --> 00:32:04,330
Princess!

296
00:32:04,330 --> 00:32:05,980
Xiaofeng!

297
00:32:12,410 --> 00:32:15,080
- Xiaofeng, don't!
- Crown Princess Consort!

298
00:32:19,360 --> 00:32:23,390
Xiaofeng, your heart is so cold.

299
00:32:23,960 --> 00:32:26,950
Why does it not warm up no matter what I do?

300
00:32:27,620 --> 00:32:30,250
Because your hands are colder than it.

301
00:32:31,200 --> 00:32:33,790
How can you warm up my heart?

302
00:32:35,440 --> 00:32:37,470
I do not believe it.

303
00:32:38,080 --> 00:32:42,950
I do not believe that you cannot understand my sincerity towards you. I do not believe that you have never loved me before.

304
00:32:47,900 --> 00:32:52,300
Xiaofeng, here! Come down first.

305
00:32:53,550 --> 00:32:55,210
Okay.

306
00:32:57,750 --> 00:33:01,500
Then tell me, you loved me before.

307
00:33:01,500 --> 00:33:03,140
Correct?

308
00:33:05,490 --> 00:33:09,030
Even if you loved me a thousand or ten thousand less than that Gu Xiaowu,

309
00:33:09,030 --> 00:33:12,150
you still loved me though. Correct?

310
00:33:12,150 --> 00:33:14,040
You tell me.

311
00:33:16,810 --> 00:33:20,610
The one I loved was only Gu Xiaowu.

312
00:33:22,400 --> 00:33:26,750
He is already dead. Dead! Do you understand?!

313
00:33:29,110 --> 00:33:32,250
My Gu Xiaowu has long been dead.

314
00:33:37,320 --> 00:33:41,440
If you never loved me, why would you hate me?

315
00:33:41,440 --> 00:33:43,800
If you only treated me as a stranger,

316
00:33:43,800 --> 00:33:46,680
then why do you have to risk your life to escape?

317
00:33:47,310 --> 00:33:52,020
Do not tell me that it is because I killed Gu Xiaowu. Before I killed Gu Xiaowu,

318
00:33:52,020 --> 00:33:56,270
when you just returned to the Eastern Palace, your gaze toward me had already changed!

319
00:33:56,270 --> 00:33:58,920
You already began to avoid me.

320
00:34:00,380 --> 00:34:02,550
Why exactly?

321
00:34:07,580 --> 00:34:09,900
I really envy you.

322
00:34:10,990 --> 00:34:14,560
You are able to never remember the things you forgot.

323
00:34:15,320 --> 00:34:19,480
Why do I repeatedly think of the things that I wish to forget?

324
00:34:20,730 --> 00:34:24,440
Why am I never able to hate the person I wish to hate?

325
00:34:28,320 --> 00:34:30,270
Li Chengyin,

326
00:34:33,620 --> 00:34:36,530
will I be the person you are never able to forget?

327
00:34:37,690 --> 00:34:40,470
Xiaofeng, tell me.

328
00:34:40,470 --> 00:34:43,010
Wh-What did I forget?

329
00:34:43,010 --> 00:34:47,040
What exactly did I forget? You... come down first.

330
00:34:47,040 --> 00:34:51,860
You tell me. I do not wish to lose you like this! Tell me!

331
00:34:53,100 --> 00:34:55,620
This time, I really will forget.

332
00:34:55,620 --> 00:34:57,660
Li Chengyin,

333
00:34:58,730 --> 00:35:00,700
I forgive you.

334
00:35:01,660 --> 00:35:05,930
I forgive all our happiness, debts,

335
00:35:05,930 --> 00:35:09,920
wild hopes, and despair.

336
00:35:09,920 --> 00:35:14,880
I choose to let go of you and to let go of myself.

337
00:35:14,880 --> 00:35:17,210
From now on,

338
00:35:17,790 --> 00:35:20,080
