339
00:35:20,900 --> 00:35:25,490
No. Xiaofeng, what really have I done wrong?

340
00:35:25,490 --> 00:35:27,980
What exactly did I do wrong?!

341
00:35:27,980 --> 00:35:30,320
What do you have to forgive me for?!

342
00:35:30,320 --> 00:35:34,430
Here! Come down first. Come down first, Xiaofeng.

343
00:35:35,690 --> 00:35:37,440
Hurry.

344
00:35:44,400 --> 00:35:47,560
- Xiaofeng!
- Crown Prince! Don't!

345
00:35:48,380 --> 00:35:50,000
Crown Prince!

346
00:35:51,100 --> 00:35:53,360
Xiaofeng!

347
00:35:54,190 --> 00:35:57,510
- Xiaofeng.
- Crown Prince.

348
00:35:57,510 --> 00:36:00,350
Xiaofeng!

349
00:36:02,100 --> 00:36:05,140
[Jade Pass]
Xiaofeng!

350
00:36:39,080 --> 00:36:42,680
