-  I am the Xi State's Ninth Princess.

351
00:36:42,700 --> 00:36:44,100
Do you know who I am?

352
00:36:44,100 --> 00:36:47,900
My father is the owner of a tea plantation.  My mother is the current empress.

353
00:36:47,940 --> 00:36:50,560
I am Gu Xiaowu from the Central Plains.

354
00:36:51,900 --> 00:36:53,950
Gu Xiaowu?

355
00:36:54,650 --> 00:36:56,370
Gu Xiaowu.

356
00:36:56,990 --> 00:37:00,420
