361
00:37:18,630 --> 00:37:22,680
These pebble stones represent the difficulties we will experience.

362
00:37:26,310 --> 00:37:28,810
Grandfather!

363
00:37:31,480 --> 00:37:34,990
I'll kill you! I'll kill you!

364
00:37:36,310 --> 00:37:39,350
Since you agreed to a marriage alliance with Li Empire, it does not matter who you marry!

365
00:37:39,350 --> 00:37:41,960
I will marry anyone but you!

366
00:37:41,960 --> 00:37:46,610
Gu Xiaowu, for generations and generations,

367
